{"tid":517033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑學業壓力困擾 屯門女生墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-01-02T02:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T06:45:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b8291001bcaed81ddd4168c7a9e031486ef0e730","tid":517033,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"早上7時26分，一名女子在屯門建盛里輕鐵蔡意橋站報案，指女兒向其同學表示要自殺，差不多同一時間，一名中學女生從屯門良景邨良偉樓高處墮下，倒卧在簷篷上昏迷不醒，保安員發現報警，救護員到場，證實女生當場死亡，警方事後封鎖現場展開調查，初步相信為同一人，疑因學業壓力尋死。據悉，女生今日學校考試，以往女生的成績一向不俗。死者的男女親屬聞訊到場認屍，傷心痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180102/57654308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57654308&d=ZGLzGSuEDofInY%2FLzkwlTAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0bd800a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57654308&h=495f90ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180102/57654308</a>"},{"pid":"5c8363cc268314c48f3c1677458f132510e56276","tid":517033,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"琴日第一跳，今日第二跳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438d4ee1ba865995995479f5e48efa03733133f6","tid":517033,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"第2件"},{"pid":"b9daaca4a12dff8438ee2bf02cd8de2e25e0ff71","tid":517033,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746edfcc41e3e6d011c6ada5cdffab744baff668","tid":51703